STATE
v.
REED 2019-0631 Supreme Court of Ohio. July 23, 2019

CASE ANNOUNCEMENT

APPEAL ACCEPTED FOR REVIEW Appellee's motion to dismiss certified-conflict appeal denied. O'Connor, C.J., and Stewart, J., concur in part and dissent in part and would grant appellee's motion to dismiss certified-conflict appeal. Donnelly, J., concurs in part and dissents in part and would decline to accept jurisdiction of the appeal. French, J., dissents.
